translate spanish Day13_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_28ae9565:

    # s "If that penlight is doing what you say it's doing, then it needs to go. It's too dangerous to keep around."
    s "Si esa linterna hace lo que dices que hace, tiene que irse. Es demasiado peligroso que siga por ahí."

# game/Kyou 13.rpy:411
