    # "So with everyone watching, I laid the penlight down on the living room table and started dismantling it in front of them."
    "Y a la vista de todas, puse la linterna en la mesa de la sala y comencé a desmantelarla delante de ellas."

# game/Kyou 13.rpy:420
translate spanish Day13_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b11c05fa:

    # "As I did so, I couldn't entirely put out of my mind the things I was potentially letting go by doing this."
    "Al hacerlo, no pude sacar completamente de mi cabeza todo a lo que potencialmente estaba renunciando por ello."

# game/Kyou 13.rpy:421
