    # "A penlight that let me reshape Nozomi's thoughts to my will?"
    "¿Una pluma linterna que me permite moldear los pensamientos de Nozomi a mi voluntad?"

# game/Kyou 13.rpy:422
translate spanish Day13_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ac760143:

    # "I kind of hate myself for it, but there's a part of me that regrets giving this up."
