# game/Kyou 13.rpy:423
translate spanish Day13_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_16fc2a7f:

    # "Not to mention the possibilities if it had worked on anyone else..."
    "Sin mencionar las posibilidades si funcionara en cualquier otra persona..."

# game/Kyou 13.rpy:426
translate spanish Day13_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6fb26203:

    # "But before too long my thoughts became irrelevant, as the penlight lay in pieces on the table."
    "Pero, poco después, mis pensamientos se vuelven irrelevantes, pues los trozos de la linterna ahora yacen en la mesa."

# game/Kyou 13.rpy:435
translate spanish Day13_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4a37ad8e:

    # s casual smile_right "I do not know what to make of this penlight's reputed ability, but I do feel a sense of relief now it's gone." with dissolve
    s casual smile_right "No sé qué pensar de la prestigiosa habilidad de esta linterna, pero siento un gran alivio al saber que se ha ido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 13.rpy:436
